sections.Trivia:
- The suspects' names are related to "participants in the Battles of Kawanakajima" and the "Twenty-Four Generals of Takeda Shingen"[1]:
Hyoe Kuroda (黒田 兵衛) comes from Kuroda Kanbei (黒田 官兵衛) ;
Mamoru Saegusa (三枝 守) comes from Saegusa Morinao (三枝 守直), real name of Saegusa Shinjuro (三枝 新十郎), and from Saegusa Moritomo (三枝 守友) ;
Shinsuke Akiyama (秋山 信介), né Aburakawa (油川), comes from Akiyama Nobutomo (秋山 信友) and Aburakawa Nobuyoshi (油川 信吉) ;
Shoji Kano (鹿野 晶次), né Tsuchiya (土屋), comes from Hajikano Tadatsugu (初鹿野 忠次) and Tsuchiya Masatsugu (土屋 昌次) ;
Shigeru Takeda (竹田 繁) comes from Takeda Nobushige (武田 信繁) ;
